  <brief_title>Comparative Trial to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of Desmopressin for the Treatment of Nocturia in Adult Women</brief_title>
  <acronym>NOC</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group, Multi-centre Trial Investigating the Efficacy and Safety of Two Different Dose Levels of Desmopressin for the Treatment of Nocturia in Adult Women</official_title>
