  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate the efficacy and safety of two different dose
      levels of desmopressin orally disintegrating tablets against placebo for the treatment of
      nocturia in adult women during 12 weeks treatment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
